c: 3
v: 159
t: "Kulwokusaasira kwa Katonda wabagondera (Gwe Muhammad) naye singa wali waboggo omuzito w'omutima bandikudduseeko, kale basonyiwe, obeegayiririre (ewa Katonda) obebuuzengako mu nsonga zonna wabula bwobanga omaliridde (n’osalawo ekyokukola) olwo nno weekwase Katonda, mazima Katonda ayagala abamwekwasa"